[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1568857&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1568857&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5727&quot; title=&quot;LBHttpSolrServer should only retry on Connection exceptions when sending updates.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-5727&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-5727&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: LBHttpSolrServer should only retry on Connection exceptions when sending updates. Affects CloudSolrServer.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
